data.text:
Global Techtron Corp, a General Corporation, is a business entity located in San Dimas, CA. Officially filed on July 19, 2019, this corporation is recognized under the document number 4299505. Governed by the California Secretary of State, the corporation maintains an active filing status.

The principal and mailing address of the corporation is situated at 960 Cienega Ave, San Dimas, CA 91773, serving as the central hub for its business operations and correspondence.

Ensuring the legal and official compliance of the corporation, Mike Liao Jr. acts as the registered agent. He operates from 960 Cienega Ave, San Dimas, CA 91773.
